<div id="box-cursos">


<!-- ************************************************************ -->
<h3>

<a href="/cursos/">Cursos do CERT<sup>&reg;</sup> Program</a>

</h3>

<p>

O CERT.br é um <a href="http://www.sei.cmu.edu/partners/"><i>Software
Engineering Institute Partner</i></a> e está <a
href="http://www.sei.cmu.edu/partners/brazilcert/">licenciado</a> para
ministrar oficialmente no Brasil os seguintes <a
href="/cursos/">cursos do CERT<sup>&reg;</sup> Program</a>: </p>

     <ul>

       <li class="interno"> <a href="/cursos/overview/"><i>Overview of
       Creating and Managing Computer Security Incident Response
       Teams</i></a>
       </li>

       <li class="interno"> <a
       href="/cursos/fundamentals-inc-handling/"><i>Fundamentals
       of Incident Handling</i></a>
       </li>

       <li class="interno"> <a
       href="/cursos/advanced-inc-handling/"><i>Advanced Incident
       Handling for Technical Staff</i></a>
       </li>

     </ul>


</div>
